{"tid":2322764,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"西環一架警車遭刑毀！","createTime":"2020-12-12T14:52:16.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-12T14:52:16.000Z","uid":44209,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"e8a5647b6c14b85476ba47b4bb2aef4b24fcbe16","tid":2322764,"uid":44209,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-12T14:52:16.000Z","msg":"可惜拉咗人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n西環發生警車被刑毀案，下午5時許，警員在西環第三街及東邊街交界將一輛警車停泊，於處理一宗投訴案件期間，一名63歲英籍男子懷疑以硬物損毀警車。警方經初步調查，以涉嫌刑事毀壞拘捕男子，案件交由西區警區刑事調查隊第二隊跟進。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/KFmuGTH.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FKFmuGTH.png&h=abe27800&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}